file: ToolCatalogResolver.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Handler\\ToolCatalogResolver"
type: final class
summary: Resolves tool catalog definitions by iterating over registered providers and aggregating their payloads. Ensures schema stability for each tool definition by computing and verifying a deterministic fingerprint.
